title: Sensunte Cabañas F.C.
text:
Sensunte Cabañas F.C. is a Salvadoran <a href="Association%20football">football</a> <a href="football%20club">club</a> based in <a href="Sensuntepeque">Sensuntepeque</a>, Cabañas, <a href="El%20Salvador">El Salvador</a>.
The club currently plays in the <a href="La%20Asociaci%C3%B3n%20Departamental%20de%20F%C3%BAtbol%20Aficionado">La Asociación Departamental de Fútbol Aficionado</a>.
